{
  "text": "One of the most important challenges in IoT managing is the devices heterogeneity that belongs the network, using many different technologies at each layer, as shown in Figure 1 . Finally, factors such as the imprecision of the collected data (e.g., RFID systems can generate between 60 and 70% of incorrect data), high data in real time, and the implicit semantics impose challenges in the configuration of IoT environments [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
